  • Constructor Details

    • Ticket

      Ticket(String title, String description)
      This constructor sets the description and title of the Ticket-object to the given parameters and sets the status to TicketStatus.NEW. This also generates a random UUID as ticketId and current date as creationDate
      Parameters:
      title - A String-value to be used as a title for this ticket
      description - A String-value describing this ticket
      See Also:
      • TicketStatus
